snippet: Tiger Woods said he fought his swing, which he had been working on for more than a year, and finished his round at the Wells Fargo Championship with a one-over-par 73.
abstract: Poor performance by Tiger Woods causes him to miss the cut at the Wells Fargo Championship golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods said he fought his swing, which he had been working on for more than a year, and finished his round at the Wells Fargo Championship with a one-over-par 73.

headline.seo: Tiger Woods Fails to Make Wells Fargo Cut
